headline: How the Story Behind WEC Energy Group Is Shifting After Recent Analyst Revisions
summary: WEC Energy Group’s stock narrative has shifted following a modest uptick in the consensus analyst price target, which has risen from $118.54 to $122.03 per share. This upward revision is attributed to analysts considering a constructive regulatory backdrop and continued strong execution by company management. However, some analysts urge caution regarding the pace of future growth. Stay tuned to discover how you can continue tracking these evolving expectations and insights for WEC Energy...
